## This is the Dockerfile for the host

```Dockerfile
FROM docker.io/alpine:3.23

RUN apk update && apk add --no-cache busybox

ENTRYPOINT [ "/bin/sh" ]
```


## Build the image

Go to the directory containing the Dockerfile and run the following command:

```bash
docker build . -t host_arazafin:p1
```

or run this command from anywhere:

```bash
docker build -t host_arazafin:p1 - <<EOF
FROM docker.io/alpine:3.23
RUN apk update && apk add --no-cache busybox
ENTRYPOINT [ "/bin/sh" ]
EOF
```
